Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:30.57,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,恭喜你！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.55,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,歡迎來到7G網路啟動儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:48.17,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你可是第七萬七千七百七十七位顧客
