Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:49.91,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:51.23,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:54.58,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,我叫中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:56.45,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,歡迎你的到來 葉香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:01:01.02,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我是全球7G委員會會長 芃伊斯·龐太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:05.96,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,葉香小姐對能夠以超級速度連接世界的7G網路有什麼期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:09.57,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,期待？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:10.00,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:13.24,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,無論何地 無論何人 都能快速被連結
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.80,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,這就是夢想中的新技術 7G
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.69,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我們沒趕上5G的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:19.64,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,而6G卻大器晚成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:22.51,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是 我們終於用7G奪回日本國的榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:24.98,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,雖然還是有些人反對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.14,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,甚至招來黑粉誹謗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.73,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是面對他們新聞學學的 我們沒有退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:33.90,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,世界最先進強大的技術 全部都包含在7G裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:37.01,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,採用全方位設備 直接將思想輸入到大腦裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.62,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,思想馬上傳遞 瞬間成真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.69,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,堪比神明的力量 就是所謂的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:44.31,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,7G
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:45.62,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,{\an8}那個 我能離開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:47.98,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.90,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就請大家一同見證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.68,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,通往未來的決定性時刻
