Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.03,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,再說了 都已經過去兩年了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:30.83,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:35.05,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這裡是吾野站區域廣播
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:40.13,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,黑豹車隊即將到達吾野學校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:47.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果您有快遞 或是需要進行購物 請及時前往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:50.66,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,欸嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.66,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,這不是和代先生和御糸婆婆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:55.22,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,有什麼奇怪的 我們倆在橋上碰見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:59.41,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我記得之前 你們不是為了一個麻袋吵了一架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.70,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,這種事情都過去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.46,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,難道你正治 還沒有跟吉根她和好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.44,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,欸 這倒也不全是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.95,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是不是還在抱怨她做的飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.03,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,她能給你做飯就不要抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:14.98,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,話是這麼說 我是灰熊 她是赤麂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.70,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我們的口味真的天差地別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.88,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,口味？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.19,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,太小家子氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.54,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.80,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,說到底 這還不是食物的問題嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.93,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.99,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,吾野可是很適合動物生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.20,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,我還聽說有些地方的人 全都變成大樹了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:29.74,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,大樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.93,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,那邊覆蓋著群山的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.32,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,能變成動物還算我們幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.62,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.72,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,變成熊之後 我總是餓的好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.70,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,要是正治你變成一棵樹就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.84,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,或者石頭 蘑菇 還有鐵線蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:42.74,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,這話說的好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.39,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,習慣之後 作為動物的生活其實也並沒有多糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.91,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,這點倒確實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.10,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我都當了兩年的熊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.66,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,早就習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.92,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,確實哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:55.24,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,之前淳史變成指猴 一直都沒適應過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:58.36,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,原來那天晚上 我看到的是淳史啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.64,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,他已經長這麼大了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.95,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,他說要是知道會發生這種事 早就離開這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.80,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,無論走到哪裡 在吾野的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.63,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,總會變成鳥類或是哺乳動物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:09.35,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:12.38,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,離不離開 都還是變成動物被困住 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.26,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.76,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,在7G事件發生前 失蹤的那個女孩還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.01,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,她現在在哪裡 做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.73,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,我記得那個叫千倉的女孩 還在尋找她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.30,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,先不說她在不在吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.57,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,但是她一個人獨自在外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.02,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,兀自一人變成一個動物 可怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.66,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,除了被動適應 還能做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:28.94,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:32.42,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,至少不用再為健康保險和養老金發愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.37,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,再者說連診所都沒剩下幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.05,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,所有的官僚早就灰飛煙滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.96,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,如果你現在走到稻荷山公園
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.28,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,還是能在那找到一個非常好的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.10,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,不過這是我聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.70,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.67,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,誰知道你走過去 到底要花上幾年時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.18,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,再說你還有沒有命能活著到那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.34,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,還有 你都不知道它們是不是人類醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.52,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,你是說人類的醫生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.13,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,可能是給人類治病的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.80,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,也可能是「人類醫生」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.87,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,啊 你說它能給人治病 但卻不是人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.02,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,他不能給人類治病 但確仍是人類 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.10,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,那個在稻荷山的高明醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就好比是「咖哩味便便」那樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你太噁心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:14.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我只是在問一個形上學的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,意義不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:19.09,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,女孩們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:22.19,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,說到咖哩 是不是肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:25.15,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,如果你們不介意 我可以分享一些蟋蟀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:26.52,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不用 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,現在吃點昆蟲也沒什麼不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要 一點也不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但聽說很有營養
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,營養到不是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:36.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,自從那次事件後 我們每年能夠收穫六次大米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,更不用說大量的苦瓜 加上我每次攝入大量熱量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,總之可愛與浪漫才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊又來了 逃避現實的情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,難道你是超·樂觀主義 做夢醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我可是 知道你想說我什麼哦 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你當我笨蛋 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.37,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好火大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.90,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不用謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.04,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼吵架絕對禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是小晶她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.54,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,被罵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:05.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,被撫子姐罵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.86,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}小晶你也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.57,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.36,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶真是個乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實也是好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.50,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.81,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,那個 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.07,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,黑豹車隊來得太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.62,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是啊 我們等了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.73,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我的小靈通收到了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.78,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說明他們應該就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,難道黑豹車隊全軍覆滅了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:28.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這下可糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的雜誌今天應該到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留她也不在這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這確實少見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:37.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,今天不是井口老師 對她進行前途職業諮詢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,前途 原來是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但現在討論這個沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.92,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,這些難過的話就別提了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:44.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,沒什麼沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.77,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這沒有什麼值得悲傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,全都是「現實」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.33,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,啊 是善治郎先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野的標誌性景觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.30,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,他以前可是很高大英俊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.72,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,兩年前他回吾野這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:59.14,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,就變成這樣只會「吧吧」這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,善治郎特別之處 是還能保持人類模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,他卻只增加了二十一歲零三個月的年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.46,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,其它人卻盡數變成了動物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:10.74,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,噢 說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:11.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:16.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們最終 也會變成某種動物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.95,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且還不能選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.59,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.60,ZH-Main-Down,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.63,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,可是都等那麼久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:24.39,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我可是好久沒有吃肉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.01,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,果然肉更加好吃 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.22,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,比起米飯 甜番薯 還有苦瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.90,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.26,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,肉真的好好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.37,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我好想吃肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:36.99,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,牛排 鮮嫩 外加上幾分生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.73,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,不對 這超級稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.47,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,可惡 我真想啃幾口生肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.27,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,等會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你這隻食慾貪婪的小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:55.74,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,欸 我剛剛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,正治先生 這樣不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:59.47,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你完全變成熊的個性了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.27,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,欸 真的嗎…別開玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.12,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留 放學之後的「加課」怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 加課？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 那完全問題不大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.46,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他問了你的前途職業選擇 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 他問我畢業之後想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我說我要「尋找她」就被說教了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:15.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你說「尋找她」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.75,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.75,ZH-Main-Down,Masaharu,0,0,0,,高先生 你是不是把它們占為己有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.24,ZH-Main-Down,Taka,0,0,0,,先到先得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.55,ZH-Main-Down,Oito,0,0,0,,腦裡只有吃肉沒有別的 真無語
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.58,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,看起來吾野這邊又要大豐收了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.31,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,貓哥 怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有什麼消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.96,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,沒有 這次又是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:05.27,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,傳言呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,比如鎮上有新面孔 或是有人離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這些傳言有沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:14.03,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,這些傳言也沒聽過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:17.00,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,能夠與外面交流的溝通點並不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:20.33,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,如果有新的人出現 這種新聞肯定會馬上傳播
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.01,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野這沒有任何要報告的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我每天都在這裡巡邏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.35,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.23,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,你們三人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.07,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,你們想要的東西 我們終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:29.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的練馬雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你不知道這是二手書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:34.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有的看就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,現在根本沒有新出版的書看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:39.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸 真的竟然找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.67,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,練馬國的愛麗絲…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這就是雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,在7G事件之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:50.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這個節目一直都在埼玉電視台 每週四晚12：30分放送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.25,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這些超現實的毒藥真的太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這也是可愛又浪漫的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:56.98,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你們說的是同一檔節目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:57.52,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,聽我說 貓哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,請讓我給你們打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.19,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,哈 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.46,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,你說什麼都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.60,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,這很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再者說我可是吾野柔道二段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:12.46,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,自從7G事件之後 熊是首先倒下的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:16.42,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,之後便是鵜鶘 袋鼠 麋鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:20.01,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,剩下僅存的我們 雖然繼續在送快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.97,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,但能堅持到什麼時候也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.03,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,如果我有什麼發現 肯定會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.26,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,好好耐心等待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.51,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,就像我找到那本書一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.06,ZH-Main-Down,Neko,0,0,0,,一切終將可能柳暗花明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不要總是想靠言語糊弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可惡 貓哥好難搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}他們走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:42.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還要再等一個月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.04,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,或者視情況等的時間會更多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:45.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子你買了什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.36,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.45,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.13,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是甜香桃木花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,甜…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:54.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,現在還能生長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:13:00.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡能種的只有大米 小麥大麥 還有苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:04.22,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是無論如何 我很想要香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是 為什麼我突然會想要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:08.90,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,到底是什麼原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,問我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,甜香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊嘞 我想是以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以小晶你買了什麼書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,作者龍彥 黑魔法書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,龍彥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,說起龍彥肯定是指澀澤龍彥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,誰會那麼肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.95,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,怎麼了 靜留姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.75,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,竟然還有出版的新報紙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,「鑽石之門逐漸放大」上面寫著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這個人 難道不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.98,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香 真的是葉香！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,蛤 這個葉香是那個葉香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還有誰能叫葉香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 這什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這是什麼時候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.39,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說是上個月的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:48.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全無法相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她為什麼會在池袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:53.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要告訴小雪奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:01.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,兩年前的那一天 世界完全改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,火車站之間的距離 城鎮之間的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:07.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,突然增加到無法跨越的長度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這不僅僅是地理的因素
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.96,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所有人和生物都發生了徹底的改變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:15.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在吾野的成年人都變成了動物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:19.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然現在還保留有人類的理性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:24.51,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但總可能有一天 會變成真正的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:28.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是吾野的情況 或許更加嚴峻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最初的時候大家都被震驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:51.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自己變成了奇怪的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:54.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,憤怒 自暴自棄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:58.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一些人組成調查小組 冒險前往別處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:02.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一半的人中途放棄折返回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剩下的一半人再也沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:10.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這可能是 她剛知道自己唯一的孫女還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,太高興了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.30,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶也沒能變能更年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.35,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,豚鼠要再過五六年可能會死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:17.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:20.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼小晶你要說這些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.16,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是玲實你提到她的年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你是真的神經大意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.93,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我只是要教你一些知識
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}要好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.55,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:40.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:47.84,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這些一切現象的變化 都是7G網路失控所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 沒有人知道如何將這一切改變回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或者說 我感覺並沒有人想要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:58.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,我做好了晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.76,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,雖然還是一如既往的苦瓜和米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,但你可要先加熱後再吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:12.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,電器之類的 應該說該感謝7G還是該譴責 總之功不可沒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:17.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們無法看電視或是上網 只有小靈通近距離能用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冰箱雖然還在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是冰箱和微波爐同時用會跳電
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:26.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們不能像以前一樣隨意地使用電能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,甚至說這到底是不是電能 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:34.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,它更像一種能量 沿著類似鐵軌傳導
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.47,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.03,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,原來靜留 你是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:42.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:44.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你那麼驚訝幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香你也是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.11,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.99,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,畢竟我就是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:52.58,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你說什麼抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我根本不知道 葉香你到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.48,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她到底什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那晚之後 再也沒見過葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:06.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也再也沒碰見過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且我也沒有找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.63,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怪不得我找不到她 原來她在池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.16,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我還以為她就在吾野附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.84,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我還苦苦尋找她了兩年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.13,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:20.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:25.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我說波奇 為什麼你沒有變成人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:28.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,既然所有人長大後都會變成動物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:30.73,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那波奇變成了人類也就不奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果葉香就在附近 波奇應該也會告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:37.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,畢竟她是你的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我怎麼從來都沒有注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.30,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生 你怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,站在這種地方可是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.94,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,帽 帽子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:00.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,母子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:04.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子的絲帶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇 這個是什麼知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.51,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎 那邊很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡面有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:47.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吧吧的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.80,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,那個可惡該死的龐太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.03,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我說了多少次要他放棄7G
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.86,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,根本不可能有人採用這種標準的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:57.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:02.27,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,威脅到物理定律 無視研究人員警告 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.28,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,只盲目接受「牟利者」提供的不可靠數據
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.38,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,而且為什麼不採用一下策 非要採用下下策
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.68,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,真的是可惡的沒用廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.30,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你不僅阻擋了我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.45,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,還用軟綿綿讓我變得軟綿綿的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.75,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,真的是不可原諒的狡猾惡徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.55,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你給我洗好屁股等著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.50,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我絕對要把7G停給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.87,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不會讓你霸占池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等會 你說池袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.16,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,對的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.89,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我不能就這樣離開池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.17,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我要馬上去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:30.31,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,看起來只有讓我平善次郎駕駛這輛兩千系列…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:31.96,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不對 等 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.57,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你是 千倉靜留對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.42,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你小的時候跌到泥溝裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎樣都行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.86,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,重要的是你是如何把兩千系列帶出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你會開火車嗎 善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.19,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你說我會不會開火車？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:45.91,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,給我再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 真的要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.52,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼帽子突然又不能把他變回來 不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:08.56,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:10.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,盡你所能 要確保自身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,謝謝你 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.73,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,如果路途中遇見了一直傲慢的狼獾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,記得叫他振作起來 快點回家裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我會如實告訴父親的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.49,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,星撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.18,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.17,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,九賀玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:26.80,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.25,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,東雲晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:28.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.45,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,中富葉香 請假缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.76,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,千倉靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.19,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,靜留她又逃跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.50,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,你們三人都不知道她在做什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:41.89,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,前天晚上 她說她解開了帽子謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,所以她圍著吾野學校跑步 和波奇一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:45.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,什麼謎團？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等會 她翹課在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.51,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不良？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留變成不良少女了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.94,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,在這裡做不良行為毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:55.14,ZH-Main-Down,Iguchi,0,0,0,,所以我認為不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,井口老師 多謝您的教導
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:00.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要退學啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:01.90,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:04.38,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.25,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:10.24,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我雖然無法和你一起去 但看起來你沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.65,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,走出這裡 去看看被7G所破壞的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.47,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我會等著你的回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:18.06,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,聽好 最重要的是保證自己的生存…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 又是半途而廢到關鍵點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:22.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:23.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我大概明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,一點也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:25.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:25.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}根本不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.94,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你已經嚇我們一大跳了 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:30.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你到底為什麼要退學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:32.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,之後就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我現在就出發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:34.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸 去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:39.64,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這可並不突然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:42.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我可是好好準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:47.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哇 竟然動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:50.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.57,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:52.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.43,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不是吧 敲 開玩笑啊
